g.text: The current screen for a failed transaction fails at multiple levels to give
a clear sense of what went wong and what the user needs to do next.
For a first time user who is trying an online platform to make a payment
the failure of order may bring a lot of anxiety.
A visual cue to indicate that the transaction has failed.
Clear Instructions as to what the user is supposed to do next
The current copy of the failure message is not good enough to ensure
the anxious user that his money is safe.
No call to action to make the transaction again, The user has to re-enter
all the details again if they wish to make the transaction again, thus
increasing the load on the user.
